# Inherit identity (GIT_AUTHOR_*, GITHUB_USER) from ~/.envrc — direnv
# doesn't walk up by default; without this the flake devShell starts with
# an empty git author.
source_up_if_exists

# Load the flake's devShell so the gitleaks pre-commit hook gets wired
# into `.git/hooks/pre-commit` on first entry. `use flake` runs the
# devShell's shellHook (provided by git-hooks.nix), which is the install
# step for the hook.
use flake
